<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-inventory-cost-structure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="124"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-inventory-cost-structure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="124">Item group</strong> – Adjustments are posted for all items that have the same item group.</li>
